sourcesContent:
import { v4 as uuidv4} from 'uuid';

const dataSlider = [
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'The Fortress of Husein-Kapetan Gradascevic',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#FF6B6C',
        width: '60%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'Medijapan visoki sjaj',
        subTitle: ' sa urezanim rukohvatima u finoj kombinaciji fronti bijela visoki sjaj i cappuccino radne ploče i zidne obloge',
        backgroundColor: 'brown',
        width: '80%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'Mosque Husejnija',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#A17C6B',
        width: '60%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'City Clock Tower',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#868B8E',
        width: '60%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'Ljiljan',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#122620',
        width: '60%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'Armored Train',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#F51720',
        width: '60%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'City Park',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#A47551',
        width: '60%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'Catholic Crkva',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#870A30',
        width: '80%',
        color: 'white',
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        title: 'Orthodox Church',
        subTitle: 'Click for More',
        backgroundColor: '#F4EBD0',
        width: '60%',
        color: 'white',
    },
]

export default dataSlider;
